
Cubix Device Numbers

Syntax:
 <major number>
  <minor number> - <description of device>, <preffered device path>

Block Devices:
 7
  0 - dummy device, /dev/loop{0,1,2,3,4}

Character Devices:
 1
  3 - Null device, /dev/null
  5 - Zero device, /dev/zero
  7 - Full device, /dev/full
  8 - Random device, /dev/random
  9 - Random device, /dev/urandom

 10
  8 - Mouse device, /dev/mouse
